OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FForce banks to offer       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmortgage help, says Labour 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government should force banks to   
OL,6, help homeowners struggling with        
OL,7, mortgage payments, Labour has said.    
OL,9,FShadow Chancellor Rachel Reeves says   
OL,10,Fborrowers should be allowed to switch  
OL,11,Fto interest-only payments for a        
OL,12,Ftemporary period to ease the crisis.   
OL,14,FMany lenders are already offering this 
OL,15,Fafter talks last year with the         
OL,16,Fgovernment, but Labour says it needs to
OL,17,Fbe enforced across the board.          
OL,19,FIt comes ahead of an expected rise in  
OL,20,Finterest rates on Thursday.            
